Package: htslibr
Type: Package
Title: A Wrapper for htslib
Version: 1.0
Date: 2019-04-08
Author: Josh Weinstock
Maintainer: Josh Weinstock <jweinstk@umich.edu>
Description: This R package wraps htslib, and can be built from a Makefile that will pull the latest htslib sourc and reconstruct the R package. Some added utilities are also included for calculating GC content and depths. 
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.1)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0
Encoding: UTF-8
StagedInstall: no
